stickers.name: orchid_order
stickers.alt: Orchid appears to have her arms crossed with a stoic expression. According to Xue, she says, 'Hand it (the manuscript) in'
stickers.caption: Hand it (the manuscript) in

stickers.name: w_www
stickers.alt: The top half of the image is filled with three rows of seven w's. The bottom half of the image is filled nine clones of W, the operator. In Chinese slang, spamming the letter w is equivalent to 'lololol.'
stickers.caption: lololololololol lololololololol lololololololol

stickers.name: w_defeat
stickers.alt: The bottom half of the image is filled nine clones of W, the operator. The entire image is put into grayscale, devoid of color and liveliness. According to Xue, the words above the sea of W read, 'Done, defeated.'
stickers.caption: Done, defeated

stickers.name: shaw_salute
stickers.alt: Shaw stands at attention in her firefighter gear and salutes enthusiastically. According to Xue, the words above her read, 'Understood!'
stickers.caption: Understood!

stickers.name: zima_threat
stickers.alt: Zima stands with her legs apart at shoulder width, her left hand on her hip and holding her axe in her right. She snarls while wearing shades. According to Xue, the words next to her read, 'Who am I hittin' today?'
stickers.caption: Who am I hittin' today

stickers.name: melantha_anxious
stickers.alt: Melantha stands while cluthing a pole near her center, her face looking like she doesn't know what to do. According to Xue, the words above her read, 'I am anxious.'
stickers.caption: I am anxious

stickers.name: durin_snooze
stickers.alt: Durin appears to be asleep with her eyes closed as she stands. A snot bubble and some snoring z's indicate Durin is definitely asleep.

stickers.name: gummy_punish
stickers.alt: Gummy smashes her frying pan over the head of a Reunion member. According to Xue, the words above them read, 'Rotten egg!' which is possibly slang for 'Scroundrel!'
stickers.caption: Scroundrel!

stickers.name: mephisto_taunt
stickers.alt: Mephisto crazily and angrily grins. He holds up his right hand and raises up one finger. In terms of positioning it looks like his index finger, but based on his personality it's probably his middle finger. According to Xue, the words next to him read, 'Aha!'
stickers.caption: Aha!

stickers.name: chen_call
stickers.alt: Ch'en sits at a desk while holding a mug in her right hand. She holds a phone to her left ear, her expression stern. According to Xue, she says, 'Lungmen Police Headquarters, how may I help you?'
stickers.caption: Lungmen Police HQ, how may I help you

stickers.name: rope_bounty
stickers.alt: Rope holds up a pair of pink boxers with white polka dots. She smiles with a mix of self-satisfaction and 'what am I doing.' According to Xue, the words above her read, 'Got it!'
stickers.caption: Got it!

stickers.name: mousse_resist
stickers.alt: Mousse holds a large sponge cake in her hands. She stares at it with yearning as drool leaks from the corner of her mouth. She sweats as she tries to resist consumption of the cake. According to Xue, the words beside her read, 'Am I not allowed?'
stickers.caption: Am I not allowed

stickers.name: kal_therapy
stickers.alt: Kal'tsit sits at a desk with her hands folded in front of her. A folded piece of paper stands on the desk, taking the shape of a nameplate, reads (according to Xue's translation), 'Psychiatrist.' According to Xue, the words beside Kal'tsit read, 'You speak, I listen. How abt that?'
stickers.caption: You speak, I listen. How abt that? [Sign: Psychiatrist]

stickers.name: haze_rest
stickers.alt: Haze sleeps under a kotatsu with her head sticking out and laying a pillow. She smiles, seemingly content. According to Xue, the words above her read, 'Resting.'
stickers.caption: Resting

stickers.name: amiya_police
stickers.alt: Amiya speaks into a walkie talkie, a speech bubble indicating that she says, '110.' For context, 110 is the Chinese equivalent of America's 9-1-1 for emergency services.
stickers.caption: (CN 110 = America's 9-1-1)

stickers.name: reunion_burn
stickers.alt: A group of three Firebomb Throwers hold up molotov cocktails. According to Xue, the word above them reads, 'BURN!'
stickers.caption: BURN!
